item.description:
Does it seem like your Python projects are getting bigger and bigger? Are you feeling the pain as your codebase expands and gets tougher to debug and maintain? Patrick Viafore is here to help us write more maintainable, longer-lived, and more enjoyable Python code.&lt;br/&gt;
